node.content: Dotties Sensitive diapers Size 3 (4-9kg) contain 34 pieces. Dotties Sensitive is the healthy diaper at home brand price! Dotties Sensitive diapers contain 0% parabens, 0% chlorine, 0% dyes, 0% lotion, 0% perfume and so no unnecessary additives so you get healthier baby buttocks. Dotties Sensitive diapers are skin-friendly and suitable for very sensitive baby skin as they are hypoallergenic, Ph neutral and dermatologically tested. The diapers are made from carefully selected raw materials of responsible origin and the production waste is maximally reused. The baby diapers give the sensitive baby skin maximum protection for 12 hours, moreover, maximum absorption ensures lower product consumption and therefore less waste.
